# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620020> (mechanical ecosystem management process)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620020> "An active ecosystem management process during which a human employs machines or tools to directly impact an ecosystem and realize some ecosystem management goal."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620020> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4366-3088>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620020> <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4817-0423>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620020> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620020> "mechanical ecosystem management process"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broadMatch> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620020> <https://w3id.org/elmo/cas/2>)
AnnotationAssertion(<https://w3id.org/elmo/property/hasCASCode> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620020> "2")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620020> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01001170>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620021> (mechanical vegetation removal process)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620021> "A mechanical ecosystem management process during which vegetation is removed."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620021> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4366-3088>)
