AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> <https://www.ontarioinvasiveplants.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/OPWG-Spading-Postcard-1.pdf>) <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620025> "A mechanical vegetation removal process in which a human severs subsoil roots using a spade and pries the plant out of the ground."@en)
