AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620831> "An environmental usage regulation process in which a competent authority establishes rules governing the timing, intensity, stocking density, or spatial distribution of livestock or herbivore grazing on a designated area, in order to prevent habitat degradation and maintain or restore ecological condition."@en)
