AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621024> "A mechanical hydrological alteration process in which a human installs subsurface tile drains to manage soil water levels, typically to reduce drainage from waterlogged soils or to control water levels on a restoration site."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621024> "Added following Delphi survey recommendations."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621024> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
