AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621025> "A mechanical hydrological alteration process in which a human installs a water control structure such as a weir, sluice gate, or stop-log to regulate water levels in a wetland, stream, or drainage ditch for ecological restoration purposes."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621025> "Added following Delphi survey recommendations."@en)
