# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621038> (assisted natural regeneration process)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621038> "A biological ecosystem management process in which a human removes or reduces stressors such as grazing pressure, invasive species, or canopy closure to facilitate the natural recovery and regeneration of native vegetation, without direct planting or seeding."@en)
