AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasRelatedSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621038> "passive ecological restoration process"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621038> "assisted natural regeneration process"@en)
