# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621039> (invasive species management process)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621039> "An active ecosystem management process in which a human targets non-native invasive species for detection, reduction, or eradication in order to protect native biodiversity and restore ecological function. The specific method employed may be biological, chemical, or mechanical."@en)
