# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621041> (aerial seeding process)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621041> "A seeding process in which a human disperses seeds over a restoration site using aircraft such as helicopters or drones, typically to access terrain that is difficult to reach on foot or to cover large areas efficiently."@en)
