AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621042> "A planting process in which a human establishes herbaceous plants, including forbs, grasses, and sedges, as rooted individuals at a restoration site."@en)
