AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621048> "A mechanical fauna deterrent process in which a human deploys sound-producing devices to deter fauna from a specific area or activity, including devices that emit distress calls, predator sounds, or ultrasonic signals."@en)
