AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621049> "A mechanical fauna deterrent process in which a human deploys visual stimuli such as effigies, reflective tape, scarecrows, or predator decoys to deter fauna from a specific area or activity."@en)
