AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621050> "A chemical application process in which a human applies a molluscicide to reduce or eliminate populations of invasive or pest molluscs, such as invasive snails or mussels, in order to protect native aquatic or terrestrial ecosystems."@en)
