AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621051> "A chemical application process in which a human applies a piscicide to reduce or eradicate fish populations in a water body, typically to remove invasive fish species prior to native fish reintroduction."@en)
