SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621055> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620630>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621056> (straw mulch addition process)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3621056> "A mulch addition process in which a human spreads straw over a restoration site to retain soil moisture, reduce erosion, moderate soil temperature, or suppress competing vegetation germination."@en)
